title: Adobe Illustrator CC Classroom in a Book 2015 + Lesson Files
description:
This is a pdf ebook copy of Adobe Illustrator CC Classroom in a Book (2015 Release), AND the lesson files from peachpit (college students will need those.) It was trivial to crack their 'verification', but that may change, so I have included the lesson file as well. That's why the download is over 300 mbs.

Remember, upload all your textbooks! College students are broke enough as it is
